data.text:
TIME SLIP: TOMORROW, NOW, & BACK AGAIN

JUNE 8 - SEPTEMBER 30, 2024

Open in addition to our Mix-Tape experience for Summer 2024, at 25 NW 9th St, Downtown OKC.

After 7 years, 6 temporary experiences, and 1 permanent experience the time has come to take the next step on the Factory Obscura immersive art journey with the opening of TIME SLIP: Tomorrow, Now, & Back Again!

TIME SLIP is Factory Obscura’s newest temporary experience taking you on a journey outside, inside, and through time. Share some time and space with us as you slip through the Past, Present, & Future of Factory Obscura. Travel the labyrinth to encounter some classic creatures while exploring and interacting with our newest creations.
